<li><a href="/wiki/Adam_Curtis" title="Adam Curtis">Adam Curtis</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/The_Century_Of_The_Self" title="The Century Of The Self" class="mw-redirect">The Century Of The Self</a></i>, a 4-part BBC TV series.</li>
