<li><a href="/wiki/Marvin_Olasky" title="Marvin Olasky">Marvin Olasky</a> column on his interview with Bernays at <a href="http://www.townhall.com/Columnists/MarvinOlasky/2006/07/27/deliver_us_from_chaos" class="external text" title="http://www.townhall.com/Columnists/MarvinOlasky/2006/07/27/deliver_us_from_chaos" rel="nofollow">Townhall.com</a></li>
</ul>
